#

Blue Cheese Burger

25 min
$12.5
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

BurgerComfort FoodBeef

Description

Juicy beef patty topped with creamy blue cheese, served on a toasted bun with fresh toppings for an unforgettable flavor experience.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • blue cheese: 4 oz
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • red onion: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
  • worcestershire sauce: 1 tbsp
